Deployed Proxmox server to virtualize machines and containers for AD environment. 
Configured pfSense firewall with Snort and Suricata for advanced threat detection and prevention.
Implemented Elasticsearch and Kibana to collect and analyze system logs for monitoring and troubleshooting. Installed Elastic Defend for better network visibility and security against 
attacks.
Deployed Active Directory for user and resource management. Configured complaint for Windows Server 2019 DC, DNS, and DHCP. Installed Windows 10, 7, Ubuntu, and 
Kali Linux client machines for compliance.
Conducted regular security audits using tools such as OpenVAS, Nessus, Nmap, Metasploit etc. Deployed Security Onion for network traffic monitoring and analyzed logs 
with Wireshark for early threat detection and prevention. 
